Package ie.gmit.sw.sprites

Class SpriteFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.gmit.sw.sprites.SpriteFactory
  • public class SpriteFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    A singleton class factory class. Instead of loading data every time it is loaded into memory once and shared between consumers.
    Author:
    Kevin Barry
